{"tid":41342,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣開始轉涼了","createTime":"2016-12-15T23:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T00:51:58.000Z","uid":33880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31985f35ec6e8187d00d583c901b5f5bcb62f0eb","tid":41342,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c7039e57e6882efe5c3228c47368ed8d095ac0","tid":41342,"uid":5844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:08:19.000Z","msg":"凍個一兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45303a3536d77b0317efafb10f1f5ec197c50a50","tid":41342,"uid":65068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:11:39.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n高登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"4e284d84bd010ac273d6373905f302856735e931","tid":41342,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凍個一兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣又熱到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7100b9bcf2f8eb9e604f117c872189cbdcf595af","tid":41342,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:45:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8831f5789ec0fef2d87b4ac3435858c150a37bb","tid":41342,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:46:47.000Z","msg":"未出門口既巴打著多件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35ced421b75c35a1098532d91525e7a6bc12537","tid":